Name: UCSB
Description: A great university located along the California coast!

Name: Disneyland Park
Description: The original Disney themepark, featuring a multitude of fun attractions, such as the recently opened Star Wars Galaxy's Edge, the classic Fantasyland, Toontown, and so much more.

Name: Cambria, CA
Description: Cambria, California is a small coastal town featuring small hotels, quality dining establishments, and several beaches such as Moonstone Beach Park.

Name: Avila Valley Barn
Description: Avila Valley Barn is a family owned farm where tourists visiting Avila Beach, CA can purchase fresh produce, fresh baked goods, enjoy grilled corn on the cob, visit the farm animal, and so much more.

Name: Aquarium of the Pacific
Description: The Aquarium of the Pacific is a public aquarium located in Long Beach, California featuring an extensive collection of aquatic and coastal animals who call the Pacific Ocean home.

Name: Sequoia National Park
Description: The Sequoia National Park is a massive expanse of mountainous forest notable for its giant sequoia trees, including the Giant Forest which is home to five of the ten largest trees on the planet.
